{
  "widgets": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 24,
      "height": 2,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "# AWS Serverless Event Pipeline Dashboard\nMonitoring API Gateway, Lambda, DynamoDB, Kinesis, and operational health for the event pipeline."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 2,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Producer Lambda - Invocations and Errors",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/Lambda", "Invocations", "FunctionName", "event-producer-console", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "Errors", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "Throttles", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 2,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Consumer Lambda - Invocations and Errors",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/Lambda", "Invocations", "FunctionName", "event-consumer-console", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "Errors", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "Throttles", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 8,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Producer Lambda - Duration",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "event-producer-console", { "stat": "Average" } ],
          [ "...", { "stat": "Maximum" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300,
        "yAxis": {
          "left": {
            "label": "Milliseconds"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 8,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Consumer Lambda - Duration",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/Lambda", "Duration", "FunctionName", "event-consumer-console", { "stat": "Average" } ],
          [ "...", { "stat": "Maximum" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300,
        "yAxis": {
          "left": {
            "label": "Milliseconds"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 14,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "DynamoDB EventTable - Write Activity",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/DynamoDB", "ConsumedWriteCapacityUnits", "TableName", "EventTable", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "WriteThrottleEvents", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "SuccessfulRequestLatency", ".", ".", "Operation", "PutItem", { "stat": "Average" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 14,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Kinesis event-stream - Incoming Records and Bytes",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/Kinesis", "IncomingRecords", "StreamName", "event-stream", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "IncomingBytes", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ],
          [ ".", "WriteProvisionedThroughputExceeded", ".", ".", { "stat": "Sum" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Kinesis Consumer Health - Iterator Age",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/Lambda", "IteratorAge", "FunctionName", "event-consumer-console", { "stat": "Maximum" } ]
        ],
        "period": 300,
        "yAxis": {
          "left": {
            "label": "Milliseconds"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "log",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Recent Producer Lambda Logs",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "query": "SOURCE '/aws/lambda/event-producer-console' | fields @timestamp, @message\n| sort @timestamp desc\n| limit 20",
        "view": "table"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "log",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 26,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Recent Consumer Lambda Logs",
        "region": "us-east-2",
        "query": "SOURCE '/aws/lambda/event-consumer-console' | fields @timestamp, @message\n| sort @timestamp desc\n| limit 20",
        "view": "table"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 26,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## Operational Checks\n\nUse this dashboard to confirm:\n\n- Producer Lambda is receiving API requests.\n- Producer Lambda errors remain at zero.\n- Events are being written to DynamoDB.\n- Events are being published to Kinesis.\n- Consumer Lambda is processing records.\n- Iterator age remains low.\n- CloudWatch logs show validation, persistence, streaming, and consumer processing."
      }
    }
  ]
}
